Package org.eclipse.launchbar.core

Interface ILaunchBarListener

public interface ILaunchBarListener
Listener that can be installed on launch bar to listen for state changes. ILaunchBarManager.addListener(ILaunchBarListener). Activator.getService(ILaunchBarManager.class).addListener(new ILaunchBarListener(){ public void activeLaunchTargetChanged(ILaunchTarget target) { // do something } });
